<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="79" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="14.[805,1406,557,885]" pageId="14" pageNumber="79">
<emphasis box="[833,977,557,583]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="79">Distribution.</emphasis>
Only known from the island of Hispaniola, in valleys (Morne de la Selle, Haiti) at ca. 1600 m. The type and one other sheet from the Dominican Republic (
<emphasis box="[1023,1243,658,684]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="79">Zanoni &amp; al. 33773</emphasis>
, not seen) are the only specimens of this species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="79" type="materials_examined">
